com.tsgrp.migration.event

Class MoveFileListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.event.MoveFileListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PostUpdateLogItemEventListener, SourceEndExportFinalNodeEventListener, TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener, TargetEndImportFinalNodeEventListener, TargetEndImportNodeEventListener

    public class MoveFileListener
extends AbstractListener
implements SourceEndExportFinalNodeEventListener, TargetEndImportNodeEventListener, TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener, TargetEndImportFinalNodeEventListener, PostUpdateLogItemEventListener
    A post import listener which moves a file or folder to a new location. Replaces the deprecated MoveProcessedFile class.
